                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Anne, what's happening in the village?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "It's not good. People are getting infected, and we're running out of supplies."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Do you know anyone who might be able to help?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "anne",
                    "line": "You might want to talk to George at the powerstation. He's been trying to keep the grid running."
